msg: Added service_exists() subroutine.  Added check to disable_windows_defender() to check if the service exists before trying to disable it to prevent warnings from appearing if it isn't installed.
Changed OK notify messages to WARNING in start_service() and stop_service() if the service doesn't exist.
Added check in set_service_startup_mode() if the service doesn't exist, displays a warning if it doesn't.
